                       Suggested Long Description

WinZip brings the convenience of Windows to the use of archivers like PKZIP
and ARJ.  It features an a powerful yet intuitive point and click drag and
drop interface for viewing, running, extracting, adding, deleting, and
testing files in ZIP, LZH, and ARC files, including self extracting
archives.  Optional virus scanning support is included.

Version 4.0 adds ARJ support, a 3-D look, a new color toolbar, and other
features.  Quotes from popular publications include:  "Repeatedly charms
you" Windows Magazine 12/92.  "Our copy gets quite a daily workout" Windows
User 11/92; "Does all your compression chores with ease" Computer Shopper
10/92; "Must-Have Shareware Treasure" Compute 10/92; "Greatly facilitates
archive file management" Windows Magazine 9/92; "Powerful Yet Intuitive" PC
World 8/92; "Hot Product" Inside Microsoft Windows 8/92; "WinApp of the
Month" PC Computing 3/92.

